<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>IT Service Contract</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 40px;
      color: #222;
    }
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .section {
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .highlight {
      background: #f4f6f8;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .signature {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 70px;
    }
    .sign {
      width: 45%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .line {
      margin-top: 50px;
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>IT Services Agreement</h1>

<p>
This agreement is entered on <strong>{{contractDate}}</strong> between:
</p>

<div class="highlight">
  <p><strong>Client:</strong> {{clientName}}</p>
  <p><strong>Service Provider:</strong> {{companyName}}</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>1. Scope of IT Services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Software development / maintenance</li>
    <li>Web & mobile application services</li>
    <li>System integration & API development</li>
    <li>Technical support & maintenance</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>2. Deliverables & Timeline</h2>
  <p><strong>Project:</strong> {{projectName}}</p>
  <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{startDate}} â€“ {{endDate}}</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>3. Confidentiality</h2>
  <p>
    Both parties agree to maintain confidentiality of business,
    technical, and personal data.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>4. Payment</h2>
  <p>Total Cost: <strong>Rs. {{amount}}</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="signature">
  <div class="sign">
    <div class="line"></div>
    <p><strong>{{clientName}}</strong></p>
    <p>Client Signature</p>
  </div>

  <div class="sign">
    <div class="line"></div>
    <p><strong>{{companyName}}</strong></p>
    <p>Company Signature</p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
